sentences.chinese: 一種房屋裝置，由兩面都附有紙或布的木框組成。

sentences.english: We can produce various wood-frame cushions with corn bracts as materials.

sentences.english: And a small cabin build there, of clay and wattles made.
sentences.chinese: 那裏有一間小房子建好，是黏土和木框建成的。

sentences.english: It was originally the movable wooden frame on the hand-mould used for paper making .
sentences.chinese: 原來是手造紙所用的手模上的活動木框。
